data.description: Welcome to this lovely east side home. As you pull up you are greeted with an abundance of greenery providing great curb appeal and extra privacy. When you walk in you will notice the saltillo tile that runs throughout most of the house. The large living room is accompanied by a wood burning fire place that's great during the cooler winter nights. The kitchen and dining room look out onto your private backyard oasis with a covered patio and swimming pool. You will notice the high block wall covered in vines that provides great privacy in the back for when you want to entertain. This house has plenty of storage with a large laundry room and storage room in the 2 car garage. The primary suite is oversized with an extra sitting area. Don't miss your opportunity to come put your personal touches on this wonderful east side home.
